"தகவலைக் காண்பிக்கும். :issue:`271`"

#: ../../CHANGES.rst:121 a0556964b78940bf9b5a0f4162da67c3
msgid ""
"Account selection screen on login page. Previously logged-in users are "
"displayed as clickable cards with photos and names for quick re-"
