#: ../references/configuration.rst:14 ce9f2fa5085648ae8bcf90b818b053d4
msgid ""
"The configuration can be written in `toml` configuration file which path is "
"passed in the :envvar:`CANAILLE_CONFIG` environment variable."
msgstr ""
"The உள்ளமைவு can be written in `toml` உள்ளமைவு கோப்பு which பாதை is passed in "
"the :envvar:`CANAILLE_CONFIG` சூழல் variable."

#: ../references/configuration.rst:28 65ad986fa87b478bbb6152989beceef4
